data.description: Indulge in pure relaxation at our latest townhome property, where you can unwind in the serene sanctuary of the luxurious Spa or enjoy a delightful barbecue session in our beautifully designed BBQ area. This charming 2-story Townhome boasts a private patio, allowing you to soak up the sun and revel in the tranquility of your own outdoor oasis. Inside, you'll find ample space with 2 spacious bedrooms, accompanied by a versatile loft that can double as an office or an inviting guest bedroom. Immerse yourself in the ultimate relaxation experience in the main bathroom, featuring a separate shower and a lavish Roman tub for a soothing soak.  The cozy Gas Fireplace in the Living Room is perfect for those cold winter nights, providing a welcoming ambiance and a charming focal point. Recent upgrades include newer carpeting, modern appliances such as Washer, Dryer, Garage Door, and an efficient Air Conditioning unit, ensuring your comfort and convenience. Plus, the 2-car garage offers ample parking space for your vehicles.   Located conveniently close to shopping centers, parks, schools, and the Trolley, this property offers easy access to a wide range of amenities and lifestyle needs within walking distance. The well maintained grounds are perfect for leisurely walks along the nearby River Walk, providing a serene atmosphere for relaxation and introspection. This remarkable property is a testament to elegance and comfort, offering an extraordinary living experience for those seeking the finest in real estate. See Virtual Tour for an overview.
